 by acid or fire<li>Shots and pebbles are not damaged by acid, cold, fire or lightning<li>Bolts can be harmed by acid (not mithril bolts)<li>Arrows can be harmed by acid or fire (not mithril arrows)</ul><li><p>When found in the dungeons, ammunition will be in quantities of 6-42 (6d7)<li><p>Mithril shot have +5 bonuses to hit and to damage</ul></div></div>

